mwBwQ">Nietzsche and Legal Theory: Half-Written Laws</i>, by Peter Goodrich, Mariana Valverde, published by <a rel="mw:WikiLink" href="./Routledge" title="Routledge" id="mwBwU">Routledge</a>, p. 5</span></li><li about="#cite_note-FOOTNOTEPearson2005430-250" id="cite_note-FOOTNOTEPearson2005430-250"><a href="./Voltaire#cite_ref-FOOTNOTEPearson2005430_250-0" rel="mw:referencedBy"><span class="mw-linkback-text">↑ </span></a> <span id="mw-reference-text-cite_note-FOOTNOTEPearson2005430-250" class="mw-reference-text"><a rel="mw:WikiLink" href="./Voltaire#CITEREFPearson2005" id="mwBwY">Pearson 2005</a>, p.<span typeof="mw:Entity" id="mwBwc"> </span>430.</span></li><li about="#cite_note-251" id="cite_note-251"><a href="./Voltaire#cite_ref-251" rel="mw:referencedBy"><span class="mw-linkback-text">↑ </span></a> <span id="mw-reference-text-cite_note-251" class="mw-reference-text"><cite class="citation book" about="#mwt814" typeof="mw:Transclusion" data-mw='{"parts":[{"template":{"target":{"wt":"cite book","href":"./Template:Cite_book"},"params":{"last":{"wt":"Schmadel"},"first":{"wt":"Lutz D."},"author2":{"wt":"International Astronomical Union"},"title":{"wt":"Dictionary of minor planet names"},"year":{"wt":"2003"},"publisher":{"wt":"Springer"},"isbn":{"wt":"978-3-540-00238-3"},"page":{"wt":"481"},"url":{"wt":"https://books.google.com/?id=KWrB1jPCa8AC&amp;pg=PA481"},"accessdate":{"wt":"9 September 2011"}},"i":0}}]}' id="mwBwg">Schmadel, Lutz D.; International Astronomical Union (2003). <a rel="mw:ExtLink" class="external text" href="https://books.google.com/?id=KWrB1jPCa8AC&amp;pg=PA481" id="mwBwk"><i id="mwBwo">Dictionary of minor planet names</i></a>. Springer. p.<span typeof="mw:Entity" id="mwBws"> </span>481. <a rel="mw:WikiLink" href="./International_Standard_Book_Number" title="International Standard Book Number" id="mwBww">ISBN</a><span typeof="mw:Entity" id="mwBw0"> </span><a rel="mw:WikiLink" href="./Special:BookSources/978-3-540-00238-3" title="Special:BookSources/9