<ul id="mwB6g"><li id="mwB6k">Morley, J., <i id="mwB6o">The Works of Voltaire, A Contemporary Version</i>, (21 vol 1901), <a rel="mw:ExtLink" class="external text" href="https://web.archive.org/web/20110727030713/http://app.libraryofliberty.org/?option=com_staticxt&amp;staticfile=show.php%3Fperson=3804&amp;Itemid=28" id="mwB6s">online edition</a></li></ul>

